OL,3,CDecision not to charge Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Csoldiers for perjury upheld
OL,6,FThe Public Prosecution Service (PPS)
OL,7,Fhas upheld its decision not to
OL,8,Fprosecute former soldiers who were
OL,9,Finvestigated for giving false evidence
OL,10,Frelating to the events of Bloody
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,FKnown as one of the darkest days of
OL,14,Fthe troubles, on Bloody Sunday 13
OL,15,Fpeople were shot dead by the Parachute
OL,16,FRegiment at a civil rights
OL,17,Fdemonstration in the Bogside area of
OL,18,FLondonderry on January 30 1972.
