OL,3,CDecision not to charge Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Csoldiers for perjury upheld
OL,6,FColum Eastwood MP expressed his
OL,7,Fdisappointment that the Bloody Sunday
OL,8,Ffamilies have again been "let down by
OL,9,Fthe state".
OL,11,FA PPS spokesperson said: "After a
OL,12,Fcareful analysis of all available
OL,13,Fevidence and the legal submissions
OL,14,Fmade by the family legal
OL,15,Frepresentatives, it has been concluded
OL,16,Fthat the evidential threshold to
OL,17,Fproceed with a prosecution has not
OL,18,Fbeen met.
