OL,4,Csoldiers for perjury upheld
OL,6,F"The standard of proof required to
OL,7,Fobtain a conviction in a criminal
OL,8,Fprosecution is high.
OL,10,F"The prosecution must establish beyond
OL,11,Fa reasonable doubt the commission of a
OL,12,Fcriminal offence by an identified
OL,13,Findividual.
OL,15,F"Prosecutors must make an independent
OL,16,Fassessment of the prospects of
OL,17,Fconviction based upon the evidence
OL,18,Fthat would be admissible in criminal
OL,19,Fproceedings.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
