OL,4,Csoldiers for perjury upheld
OL,6,F"It is recognised that this outcome
OL,7,Fdoes not reflect the hopes and
OL,8,Fexpectations of the Bloody Sunday
OL,9,Ffamilies, and that it will come as
OL,10,Fanother deeply disappointing day after
OL,11,Fdecades of seeking justice for their
OL,12,Floved ones.
OL,14,F"We would further emphasise that
OL,15,Ftoday's decisions in no way diminish
OL,16,Fthe findings by the Bloody Sunday
OL,17,FInquiry.
