OL,6,F"A public inquiry and a criminal trial
OL,7,Fare very different processes and much
OL,8,Fof the material upon which the Inquiry
OL,9,Fcould rely would not be available to
OL,10,Fthe prosecution having regard to the
OL,11,Frules of evidence
OL,13,Fthat apply to criminal proceedings."
OL,15,FResponding to the decision, Colum
OL,16,FEastwood MP said: "It's impossible to
OL,17,Foverstate the scale of the burden that
OL,18,Fhas been placed on the families of the
OL,19,Fdead and injured on Bloody Sunday.
