OL,6,F"Today, again, they have been badly
OL,7,Flet down by the incredible decision
OL,8,Fnot to prosecute soldiers for perjury
OL,9,Fduring the Widgery and Saville
OL,10,FInquiries.
OL,12,F"For more than fifty years, they have
OL,13,Fhad to fight every conceivable
OL,14,Finstitution of the state for truth,
OL,15,Fjustice and accountability...
